      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "FBI, LOS ANGELES",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "DIRECTOR AND SACS HOUSTON, CINCINNATI URGENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "ATTENTION INSPECTOR [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "FLYING DISK, [REDACTED] COMPLAINT. RE HOUSTON TELETYPE [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "DEC. TWENTY EIGHT. MR. [REDACTED] LA, PRESENTLY IN ARIZONA, EXACT WHEREABOUTS UNKNOWN TO HIS",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "OFFICE, EXPECTED TO CALL MORNING OF DEC. TWENTY NINE. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "[REDACTED] MANUFACTURING COMPANY, SOUTH PASADENA, CALIF. ADVISED HE",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "AND [REDACTED] PURCHASED AIRPORT IN MOJAVE DESERT NEAR HELENDALE,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "CALIF. STATED THAT IN EARLY PART OF DEC. EXACT DATE UNKNOWN, [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "ADVISED HIM HE HAD FOUND A FLYING DISK ON THEIR AIRPORT. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "[REDACTED], AND [REDACTED] PROCEEDED TO AIRPORT WHERE THEY",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "LOCATED DISK, TOOK PICTURES OF IT AND REMOVED [REDACTED] PORTIONS",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "OF DISK, [REDACTED] RETAINING SOME PARTS AND [REDACTED] KEEPING",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "SOME PORTIONS WHICH ARE STILL IN HIS POSSESSION. [REDACTED] ADVISED",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "THAT DAY AFTER LOCATING THE DISK AN EMPLOYEE OBSERVED PARTS RETAINED",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "BY [REDACTED], AND STATED HE BELIEVED THE OBJECT HAD BEEN MANUFACTURED",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "BY [REDACTED] LA.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "STATED HE THEN CONTACTED [REDACTED] AND [REDACTED] WHO STATED THEY WERE FIN-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "ANCING [REDACTED] LA IN DEVELOPING A KITE FOR [REDACTED] SALE",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "ON OPEN MARKET AS A TOY. [REDACTED] STATED HE HAD PREVIOUSLY GIVEN",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "[REDACTED] PERMISSION TO USE HIS PRIVATE AIRPORT AT ANY TIME.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "[REDACTED] TOLD [REDACTED] THEY HAD TAKEN EXPERIMENTAL KITES TO [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
